| Layer | What | ACP/A2A Alignment |
|-------|------|-------------------|
| **Types** | `AgentCard`, `Skill`, `Capabilities`, `RoutingConfig`, `SessionMode`, `RoutingDecisionRecord`, `CandidateScore` | Matches ACP OpenAPI spec with camelCase JSON |
| **AgentMode** | Now has `skills: Vec<Skill>` + `routing: RoutingConfig` | Maps to Agent Manifest structure |
| **Classifier** | `ModeDescriptor` carries skills + priority; LLM prompt includes skill details/tags/examples | Skills-based routing per ACP/A2A |
| **Router** | Produces `RoutingDecisionRecord` per request (timestamp, candidates, latency, strategy) | Matches registry Decision Record pattern |
| **Server** | `GET /.well-known/agent.json`, `GET /agents?skill=X&tag=Y`, `GET /routing/record` | ACP discovery + registry search |
