# 🦆 Goose Project — Complete Architecture Overview

## High-Level Summary

**Goose** is an open-source AI agent framework built in Rust by Block (parent of Square, CashApp, Tidal). It provides a multi-provider, extensible agent that can use tools via the **Model Context Protocol (MCP)**, with both a CLI and Electron desktop interface.

**Version:** 1.23.0 | **Rust:** 1.92 (edition 2021) | **License:** Apache-2.0

